<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 6:24
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='373000' id='t-373000'>If you'll recall, prior to that time,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='375000' id='t-375000'>no matter what ailed you, you went to see the barber surgeon</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='378000' id='t-378000'>who wound up cupping you,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='380000' id='t-380000'>bleeding you, purging you.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='382000' id='t-382000'>And, oh yes, if you wanted,</span>
