<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 7:03
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='412000' id='t-412000'>And this particular painting, I think,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='415000' id='t-415000'>represents the pinnacle, the peak, of that clinical era.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='418000' id='t-418000'>This is a very famous painting:</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='420000' id='t-420000'>&quot;The Doctor&quot; by Luke Fildes.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='423000' id='t-423000'>Luke Fildes was commissioned to paint this by Tate,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='426000' id='t-426000'>who then established the Tate Gallery.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='428000' id='t-428000'>And Tate asked Fildes to paint a painting</span>
