<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='432000' id='t-432000'>And it's interesting that Fildes picked this topic.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='435000' id='t-435000'>Fildes' oldest son, Philip,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='438000' id='t-438000'>died at the age of nine on Christmas Eve</span>
