<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='485000' id='t-485000'>for the real patient who's in the computer.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='488000' id='t-488000'>I've actually coined a term for that entity in the computer.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='491000' id='t-491000'>I call it the iPatient.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='493000' id='t-493000'>The iPatient is getting wonderful care all across America.</span>
