 9:09
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='538000' id='t-538000'>Now I've been influenced in this thinking</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='541000' id='t-541000'>by two anecdotes that I want to share with you.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='544000' id='t-544000'>One had to do with a friend of mine who had a breast cancer,</span>
