<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 9:45
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='574000' id='t-574000'>And I pressed her, and I asked her,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='576000' id='t-576000'>&quot;Why did you come back and get your care here?&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='579000' id='t-579000'>And she was reluctant to tell me.</span>
