<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='631000' id='t-631000'>And to her, that spoke of a kind of attentiveness that she needed.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='635000' id='t-635000'>I was very influenced by that anecdote.</span>
</span>
