10:48
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='637000' id='t-637000'>I was also influenced by another experience that I had,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='640000' id='t-640000'>again, when I was in Texas, before I moved to Stanford.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='643000' id='t-643000'>I had a reputation</span>
