<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='685000' id='t-685000'>And so I hit on this method</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='687000' id='t-687000'>where I invited the patient</span>
