<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='725000' id='t-725000'>And I remember my very first patient in that series</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='729000' id='t-729000'>continued to tell me more history</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='731000' id='t-731000'>during what was meant to be the physical exam visit.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='734000' id='t-734000'>And I began my ritual.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='736000' id='t-736000'>I always begin with the pulse,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='738000' id='t-738000'>then I examine the hands, then I look at the nail beds,</span>
